Market Visualization Prototype

![Prototype Animation](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/10627606/14259824/5a0737d0-fa6e-11e5-93db-087df92f4ca4.gif)

Read my white paper [here](https://github.com/ryanpstauffer/market-vis/files/203158/White.Paper.-.Financial.Market.Data.Visualization.pdf).
